	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Have any of you guys finding someone to do a lets play of your homebrew game?<br /><br />I'm trying to get find an experienced gamer to do a blind playthrough and make a <br />LP video of it so I can see how a someone completely new to the game reacts and plays, and how <br />intuitive the controls are.<br /><br />Unfortunately the let's play forums I've been to are hostile towards any type of <br />&quot;interest checks&quot; or requests to LP a game so there is no way to enlist help on those<br />forums.<br /><br />Emailing/PMing my favorite LPers has not worked either.<br /><br />Any ideas as to how I could find someone to do this.<br /><br />-Sedwave<br />Hiatus Ward Alpha: <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.nesworld.com/homebrew/hiatwrd0.zip">http://www.nesworld.com/homebrew/hiatwrd0.zip</a><!-- m -->

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


