		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />This game is glitchy as hell.  The title screen being so glitchy leaves a terrible impression.  You need to find better ways to make the game not show areas that are being drawn on.  For example, try disabling rendering while the screen contents are being redrawn, then have the next NMI enable rendering again.<br /><br />I'm also not a big fan of the jumping sprite, she is leaning too far forward.

		

